Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.checkbox

Interface CheckboxService

All Superinterfaces:
Insertion
All Known Implementing Classes:
CheckboxServiceImpl
public interface CheckboxService extends Insertion
Provides service-level methods for interacting with checkbox UI components.

This interface defines operations to select, deselect, and verify the state of checkboxes, delegating the actual interactions to specific implementations based on the configured CheckboxComponentType.
